# Sidecar binary for Tauri's externalBin, provisioned per target triple:
#   mainframe-daemon-<triple> — Rust daemon (scripts/provision-rust-daemon.mjs)
# Real binary is MB-scale and platform-specific — never committed. cargo check
# does not need it; `tauri build` does, so provision first. Only this
# .gitignore + README.md are tracked.
#
# node-* also ignored: a stale local artifact from the retired Node sidecar
# (packages/app-tauri no longer provisions one); harmless leftover on disk.
mainframe-daemon-*
node-*
!.gitignore
!README.md
